## Limitations

The analysis is based on available literature and studies, which may not cover all aspects of the debate. The effectiveness of online learning can vary significantly depending on the subject matter, the quality of the online platform, and the individual learner's preferences and circumstances. Additionally, the rapid evolution of technology means that findings can quickly become outdated.

